  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.8.5">
<l>iḻaiyā ṭukoṅkait talainañ camuṇṭiṭ ṭiḷaṅkaṉ ṟukoṇṭu viḷaṅkā yeṟintu</l>
<l>taḻaivā ṭavantāḷ kurunta mocittut taṭantā maraippoy kaipukkā ṉiṭantāṉ</l>
<l>kuḻaiyā ṭavallik kulamā ṭamāṭē kuyilkū vanīṭu koṭimā ṭamalku</l>
<l>maḻaiyā ṭucōlai mayilā lunāṅkūr, maṇimā ṭa<supplied>k</supplied>kōyil vaṇaṅkeṉ maṉaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, worship at Maṇimāṭa Temple in Nāṅkūr, where peacocks cry</l>
<l rend="indent">in groves where clouds drift,</l>
<l>Where mansions with tall banners abound, as clusters of creepers sway,</l>
<l rend="indent">as leaves sway, and as cuckoos call nearby,</l>
<l>The place of the one who entered a wide lotus pond,</l>
<l rend="indent">having sucked up the poison at the tip of the breasts where jewels swayed,</l>
<l>Having grabbed a young calf and thrown it for woodapples, and having broken</l>
<l rend="indent">a lime tree with a stout trunk so that its leaves withered.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
